    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 372,
      "width": 344,
      "height": 172,
      "text": "At least 1 = Total - None\nAt most k = C(0)+C(1)+...+C(k)\nnC0+nC1+...+nCn = 2^n\nPascal: nCr + nC(r-1) = (n+1)Cr\nDerangement D(n): 0,1,2,9,44,265\nD(n) = (n-1)[D(n-1)+D(n-2)]\n\nWHY: 2^n = total subsets of n items;\n  each item is either in or out (2 choices).\n\nEx: n=4 → 2^4=16 total subsets",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 14,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "At least 1 = Total - None\nAt most k = C(0)+C(1)+...+C(k)\nnC0+nC1+...+nCn = 2^n\nPascal: nCr + nC(r-1) = (n+1)Cr\nDerangement D(n): 0,1,2,9,44,265\nD(n) = (n-1)[D(n-1)+D(n-2)]\n\nWHY: 2^n = total subsets of n items;\n  each item is either in or out (2 choices).\n\nEx: n=4 → 2^4=16 total subsets",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
