      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 5 letters, pick & arrange 3\nStep 2: 5P3 = 5!/(5-3)! = 120/2 = 60\n\nTRICK:\nSlot method: fill slots left to right\n  ┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐\n  │ 5 ││ 4 ││ 3 │ = 60\n  └───┘└───┘└───┘\n  1st  2nd  3rd\n\nAnswer: 60 ways ✓",
