    {
      "id": "el_35",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1086,
      "width": 252,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SELECT → nCr, ARRANGE → nPr\n  10C4 = (10×9×8×7)/24 = 210\n  10P4 = 10×9×8×7 = 5040\n\nTRICK:\nnPr = nCr × r!\n5040 = 210 × 24 ✓\nJust check: does ORDER matter?\nYes→nPr  No→nCr\n\n  SELECT(nCr)──×r!──>ARRANGE(nPr)\n  210     ──×24──>   5040\n\nAnswer: Select=210, Arrange=5040 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3500,
      "version": 1,
