      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: SELECT → nCr, ARRANGE → nPr\n  10C4 = (10×9×8×7)/24 = 210\n  10P4 = 10×9×8×7 = 5040\n\nTRICK:\nnPr = nCr × r!\n5040 = 210 × 24 ✓\nJust check: does ORDER matter?\nYes→nPr  No→nCr\n\n  SELECT(nCr)──×r!──>ARRANGE(nPr)\n  210     ──×24──>   5040\n\nAnswer: Select=210, Arrange=5040 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
