      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1102,
      "width": 267,
      "height": 173,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 6 distinct letters → 6!\nStep 2: = 720\n\nTRICK:\n  ┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐\n  │ 6 ││ 5 ││ 4 ││ 3 ││ 2 ││ 1 │= 720\n  └───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘\nStart with D: fix D → 5! = 120\nStart D, end N: fix both → 4! = 24\n\nAnswer: 720 ways ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
