        "type_5"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 6 distinct letters → 6!\nStep 2: = 720\n\nTRICK:\n  ┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐\n  │ 6 ││ 5 ││ 4 ││ 3 ││ 2 ││ 1 │= 720\n  └───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘\nStart with D: fix D → 5! = 120\nStart D, end N: fix both → 4! = 24\n\nAnswer: 720 ways ✓",
