    {
      "id": "el_45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1086,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 216,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: M=1, I=4, S=4, P=2 → 11 letters\nStep 2: 11!/(1!×4!×4!×2!)\n  = 39916800/1152 = 34650\n\nTRICK:\nn! / (repeat factorials)\nDivide by each repeated letter's factorial\nBALLOON: 7!/(2!×2!) = 1260\n\n  M I S S I S S I P P I\n  1 4    4      2  =11\n  11! / (1!×4!×4!×2!)\n\nAnswer: 34650 ways ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
