      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If 12 people shake hands with each other exactly once, how\nmany handshakes occur? Also, how many diagonals does a\n10-sided polygon have?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_64",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1888,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 64,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_65",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1910,
      "width": 288,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Handshakes = 12C2 = 12×11/2 = 66\nStep 2: Diagonals = 10C2 - 10\n  = 45-10 = 35\n\nTRICK:\nHandshakes = n(n-1)/2\nDiagonals = n(n-3)/2\n12 people: 12×11/2 = 66\n10-gon: 10×7/2 = 35\n\n  A──B  Each pair shakes once\n  |\\/|  nC2 = n(n-1)/2\n  |/\\|  Diag = nC2 - n sides\n  C──D\n\nAnswer: Handshakes=66, Diag=35 ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 65,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Handshakes = 12C2 = 12×11/2 = 66\nStep 2: Diagonals = 10C2 - 10\n  = 45-10 = 35\n\nTRICK:\nHandshakes = n(n-1)/2\nDiagonals = n(n-3)/2\n12 people: 12×11/2 = 66\n10-gon: 10×7/2 = 35\n\n  A──B  Each pair shakes once\n  |\\/|  nC2 = n(n-1)/2\n  |/\\|  Diag = nC2 - n sides\n  C──D\n\nAnswer: Handshakes=66, Diag=35 ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
