    {
      "id": "el_80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2321,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 202,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Odd → units = 1,3,5 (3 choices)\nStep 2: Fill restricted spot first!\n  Remaining 3 spots from 4 digits\n  = 3 × 4×3×2 = 72\n\nTRICK:\nFill restricted position FIRST\n  ┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐\n  │ 4 ││ 3 ││ 2 ││ 3 │ = 72\n  └───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘\n              Units(odd)\n\nAnswer: 72 ways ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
