      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Odd → units = 1,3,5 (3 choices)\nStep 2: Fill restricted spot first!\n  Remaining 3 spots from 4 digits\n  = 3 × 4×3×2 = 72\n\nTRICK:\nFill restricted position FIRST\n  ┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐┌───┐\n  │ 4 ││ 3 ││ 2 ││ 3 │ = 72\n  └───┘└───┘└───┘└───┘\n              Units(odd)\n\nAnswer: 72 ways ✓",
