    {
      "id": "el_90",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2321,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Circular: (n-1)! = 7! = 5040\nStep 2: Necklace: flip = same\n  = 5040/2 = 2520\n\nTRICK:\nNecklace = (n-1)!/2\nLine: n! | Circle: (n-1)!\nNecklace: (n-1)!/2 (extra /2 for flip)\n= 7!/2 = 2520\n\n  ○─○─○─○    Flip gives same\n  │     │    necklace, so /2\n  ○─○─○─○\n\nAnswer: 2520 ways ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 90,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_15"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Circular: (n-1)! = 7! = 5040\nStep 2: Necklace: flip = same\n  = 5040/2 = 2520\n\nTRICK:\nNecklace = (n-1)!/2\nLine: n! | Circle: (n-1)!\nNecklace: (n-1)!/2 (extra /2 for flip)\n= 7!/2 = 2520\n\n  ○─○─○─○    Flip gives same\n  │     │    necklace, so /2\n  ○─○─○─○\n\nAnswer: 2520 ways ✓",
