    {
      "id": "el_95",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2779,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: All misplaced → Derangement\nStep 2: D(4) = 4![1-1+1/2-1/6+1/24]\n  = 24 × 3/8 = 9\n\nTRICK:\nMemorize: D(1)=0 D(2)=1 D(3)=2\nD(4)=9 D(5)=44 D(6)=265\nRecurrence: D(n) = (n-1)[D(n-1)+D(n-2)]\nD(4) = 3×(2+1) = 9\n\n  Letter:    L1 L2 L3 L4\n  Envelope:  E1 E2 E3 E4\n  NO letter in its own envelope!\n  D(4) = 9 such arrangements\n\nAnswer: 9 ways ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 9500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 95,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_16"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: All misplaced → Derangement\nStep 2: D(4) = 4![1-1+1/2-1/6+1/24]\n  = 24 × 3/8 = 9\n\nTRICK:\nMemorize: D(1)=0 D(2)=1 D(3)=2\nD(4)=9 D(5)=44 D(6)=265\nRecurrence: D(n) = (n-1)[D(n-1)+D(n-2)]\nD(4) = 3×(2+1) = 9\n\n  Letter:    L1 L2 L3 L4\n  Envelope:  E1 E2 E3 E4\n  NO letter in its own envelope!\n  D(4) = 9 such arrangements\n\nAnswer: 9 ways ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
